  </div>
  {/* Work Exp */}
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-2" style={{ gridArea: "b" }}>
    <h2 class="hl text-xl mr-auto ml-2">Work Exp 4 years</h2>
    <p class="ml-10">1y Engineer in ITSM</p>
    <p class="ml-10">1y FullStack (Java/Scala)</p>
    <h2 class="hl text-xl ml-10">2 years Frontend Dev</h2>
    <article class="article flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-end flex-wrap">
        <h4 class="text-md mr-2">A Few Projects</h4><p>Outsourced at</p>
        <h3 class="hl italic text-md self-end relative ml-auto">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.digitalleague.ru/"
            >Digital League</a
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
      <p>
        TypeScript, React, Angular, Ant Design, Material Design, Redux, SCSS,
        Formik, React-Hook-Form
      </p>
      <ul class="ul">
        <li>
          <span
            >Developed several web applications for external clients, primarily
            using <b>React</b>. Rebuilt a legacy <b>Angular</b> calendar widget that
            integrates in Naumen SD</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Collaborated in cross-functional teams (frontend/backend
            developers, designers, project managers) across various client
            projects, following <b>Agile</b> workflows</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Solo development. Transformed <b>Figma</b> designs into functional prototypes
            for client <b>presentations</b> at major financial company</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Created a <b>TypeScript</b> utility type to narrow object fields by
            their type for <b>react-hook-form</b> component</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Developed a mini-app that controls outer ITSM application to
            reconfigure default behavior, to enhance visual aspects</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="article flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap">
        <h4 class="text-md">Corporate Device Detection App</h4>
        <h3 class="hl italic text-md ml-auto">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.alloysoftware.com/"
            >Alloy Software</a
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
      <p>
        TypeScript, React, Material Design, Zustand, Tanstack/Query,
        Tanstack/React-Virtual, React-Hook-Form, Cypress
      </p>
      <ul class="ul">
        <li>
          <span
            >As my first task in the company, I had to migrate the project from <b
              >Formik</b
            > to <b>react-hook-form</b> and then migrate from <b
              >styled-components</b
            > to <b>MUI sx</b> approach</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Optimized large datasets using <b>tanstack/react-virtual</b> and with
            server-side pagination, reducing DOM load and request time</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            ><b>E2E tests. Cypress</b> was added and I wrote most E2E test case scenarios
            for every section of the project</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Actively worked with GitLab <b>CI/CD</b> pipelines (debugging failed
            tests)</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <span
            >Enforced clean <b>Git</b> history via <b>rebase/squash</b> practices</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
